<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="S" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Shriek2" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Shriek,</orth> vb. to scream: <bibl n="shak. luc 307" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 307</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tmp 5.233" default="NO" valid="yes">Tp. V, 233</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.1.309" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. I, 1, 309</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 1.2.78" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. I, 2, 78</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. wt 5.1.65" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. V, 1, 65</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 5.3.190" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. V, 3, 190</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jc 2.2.24" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. II, 2, 24</bibl>. Per. <bibl n="shak. jc 3.0." default="NO" valid="yes">III Prol. 51</bibl>. Used of the cry of the owl: <bibl n="shak. ven 531" default="NO" valid="yes">Ven. 531</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. pht 5" default="NO" valid="yes">Phoen. 5</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. r2 3.3.183" default="NO" valid="yes">R2 III, 3, 183</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 5.6.44" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C V, 6, 44</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. jc 1.3.28" default="NO" valid="yes">Caes. I, 3, 28</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 2.2.3" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. II, 2, 3</bibl>. With <cit><quote>out:</quote> <bibl n="shak. r3 1.4.54" default="NO" valid="yes">R3 I, 4, 54</bibl></cit> (Qq <emph>squeaked</emph>). Transitively: <cit><quote>--ing undistinguished woe,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lc 20" default="NO" valid="yes">Compl. 20</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>